{"nodes": [{"id": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design", "label": "MCP Server Design Spec", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_mcp_server_module", "label": "In-App MCP Server (src/bun/mcp)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Lives in the Bun main process because it already holds the GitLab credentials and client, so GitLab tools are a direct reuse. SDK Server + StreamableHTTPServerTransport chosen over a hand-rolled protocol (protocol/validation risk) and over proxying into the webview (couples to a live webview and reactive composables). HTTP fits a long-running GUI; stdio deferred."}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_tool_registry", "label": "MCP Tool Registry", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "ToolDef { name, description, inputSchema, handler }; lumen_<domain>_<verb> naming; the registry answers tools/list and dispatches tools/call with validated args. Destructive MR merge intentionally excluded in v1."}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_auth_gate", "label": "MCP Auth Gate (127.0.0.1 + Bearer)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Safe by default: off by default, opt-in via Settings, localhost-only bind, generated bearer token rejected with 401 before the request reaches the SDK; port-in-use surfaces an error rather than silently roaming."}, {"id": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_app_control_bridge", "label": "App-Control Bridge (reportAppState + command push)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Built from the two proven RPC directions \u2014 no new framework capability: the webview pushes state snapshots via a reportAppState handler (read tools return the cache instantly, no synchronous round-trip), and the host drives the webview via executeJavascript dispatching lumen:mcp-command CustomEvents. Drives are fire-and-forget; the agent re-reads lumen_app_state to confirm."}], "edges": [{"source": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_mcp_server_module", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_tool_registry", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_auth_gate", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design", "target": "specs_2026_06_09_mcp_server_design_app_control_bridge", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-09-mcp-server-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "s